Eternal Void Engine Installation Instructions
=============================================

Currently only Linux x86_64 is supported, but this software is made using
cross-platform technologies, so other platforms will be supported in the future.

Linux:
	Compile:
		$ mkdir build
		$ cd build
		$ cmake ..
		$ make
		$ ./eternal-void-engine

	Optional Install (NOT IMPLEMENTED YET!!):
		$ sudo make install
		$ cd ~
		$ eternal-void-engine